			<h1 style="font-size: 2em;"><span class="eyebrow">Mission of Hope Haiti</span>
			<br />
			Request information about SHORT-TERM MISSION TRIPS</h1>
			<p>
			If you would like to learn more about how you or a group can serve on a short-term mission trip with Mission of Hope, Haiti, please fill out and submit the form below. Once we have received your request, our Mission Trips Coordinator will be in touch with you.
			</p>
			<div class="forms">
				<% if @isvalid.nil?%>
